<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7301> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7301" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Pr. before 73. Since C. Licinius Sacerdos (154). Pr. 75, is listed after him in the consilium of 73 (SIG(3) 747; Sherk, RDGE no. 23, 133-138; see MRR 2.114-115), he was probably father or older brother, already a praetorius, of the praetor of 73, and his praetorship, though later than that of Marcellus, may be several years earlier. See L. R. Taylor, VDRR 204; Badian, Historia 12, 1963, 138, on SIG(3) 747." .
